name: Grace Bay Beach
description: An absolutely idyllic setting. Golden sand edging crystal clear blue water with gently lapping waves - it's what postcards were made for.

name: Varadero Beach
description: Postcard perfect. The water was the bluest I’ve ever seen and the sand was powdery white.

name: Turquoise Bay
description: Words cannot capture how spectacular this beach is. Long stretches of white sand and crystal blue water. World class snorkeling for beginners as well as experienced.

name: Quarta Praia
description: Warm water with amazing views. When the sea calms down it forms amazing natural pools. When in Morro de São Paolo this beach is a must see.

name: Eagle Beach
description: Tranquil and pristine, the water is beautifully clear with no rocks or seaweed. The beach stretches as far as you can see.

name: Radhanagar Beach
location: Havelock Island, Andaman and Nicobar Islands
description: Amazing clear turquoise water, mangrove forests in the background, pristine white sand and not too deep... what's not to like!

name: Baia do Sancho
description: A beautiful remote beach that can only be reached by descending ladders and stone steps. The majestic bluffs will take your breath away.

name: Trunk Bay Beach
location: Virgin Islands National Park, St. John
description: Great snorkeling with lobster, tarpon, squid, sea turtles and a beautiful beach, great place at sunset.

name: Baia dos Golfinhos
description: Whenever you go, there's no doubt you'll see dolphins! But the landscape alone is breathtaking.

name: Spiaggia dei Conigli
description: One of the marvels of the world. White sand beach, turquoise water, cooling sea breeze. Prepare for a 20-minute walk to get to the beach, but once you are there you feel like you're not on Earth.

name: Cable Beach
description: The sunsets are amazing, spacious grassed picnic areas, iconic camel rides and beach side restaurants.

name: Praia da Falesia
description: Gorgeous red sand cliffs lead to the green-blue ocean and a white sand beach that seemingly stretches forever.

name: Hapuna Beach State Recreation Area
description: There is a small set of rocks that provided some of the best snorkeling we saw on the island! The water was crystal clear and the brightly colored tropical fish plentiful.

name: Siesta Beach
description: Absolutely beautiful beach with silky quartz sand! Great beach for people watching, sunsets, breakfast/morning walk on beach and finding sand dollars.

name: Maho Bay Beach
description: A beautiful white sand beach known for snorkeling with sea turtles. We saw countless turtles and an octopus while snorkeling just off the beach.

name: Poipu Beach Park
description: There was amazing snorkeling area, a small beach shielded from the waves for the little ones, and surfing all within a short distance of each other.

name: Playa de Muro Beach
description: Playa de Muro has a wonderful, sandy beach with a warm, clear turquoise sea. Ideal for children because of its gentle, shallow waters.

name: Playa Manuel Antonio
description: Beautiful beach with patches of sparkly black sand and very few waves, idyllic to float and bask.

name: Playa Norte
description: The water is clear and every beautiful shade of blue you can imagine. It’s the very essence of true paradise.

name: Nungwi Beach
description: Amazing combination of white, velvet-like sands and water changing colors throughout the day, from light blue to emerald green.

name: Magens Bay
description: Beautiful Beach! Gorgeous colors! Great snorkeling right off the beach. Bring flippers if you want to get out a bit further to see some turtles.

name: Nissi Beach
description: Longish sweeping beach with lovely clear warm water with various tavernas along the way. Loads of sunbeds with umbrellas.

name: Bavaro Beach
description: The water is as crystal clear as you see in a magazine and the beach is well maintained with no rocks. A place of total relaxation.

name: Balos Lagoon
description: Feels like another planet. A breathtaking place with a lagoon on one side and a beach on the other.

name: Yonaha Maehama Beach
description: It’s a beach you can dream about. A lot of sand, clear and warm water and these views. It’s a perfect vacation spot.

name: The Old Stamp House Restaurant
description: All the staff want you to enjoy every moment of every course. Knowledge and love of food and where and how it is sourced. And you will enjoy every mouthful.

name: Oro Restaurante
description: Amazing tasting menu, with unique combinations of flavors and very creative presentation. They make drinks based on your preferences, which is fun. A place for a long, lingering, expensive meal.

name: Madonnina del Pescatore
description: Beautiful location, amazing food and wine, pure theatre. The level of service, the quality of the food, the artistry and imagination make this an unforgettable experience. A joyous afternoon.

name: Martin Berasategui
description: The best combinations of flavors we have ever experienced. The meal was culinary poetry.

name: El Xato
description: Fantastic food, great wine, wonderful service. The food was beautiful and thoughtful in presentation. Every dish showcased the ingredients brilliantly and every mouthful was delicious.

name: Ristorante Villa Crespi
description: Peerless from start to finish. What could have been an intimidating experience was rendered warm, engaging and friendly by the terrific team.

name: Guillaume Scheer - Les Plaisirs Gourmands
description: The name of the restaurant says it all: pure pleasure, from the fabulous, well presented and tasteful dishes to the wine selection and discreet though friendly service.

name: Sachi Heliopolis
description: Lovely elegant restaurant in Heliopolis with calm, stylish dark interiors and fabulous service. Each dish was better than the last.

name: Auberge Du Vieux Puits
description: Truly a dream. From local ingredients, the chef conjures up aromas, textures and flavors you've never experienced. The stuff of legend. WOW!

name: Paul Ainsworth at No
description: Simply outstanding. The inventiveness of the food and the depth of flavours and textures were amazing. Everything was just delicious.

name: La Colombe
description: Can I award six stars? I will have to find a thesaurus to adequately describe the food. The service was also beyond fault.

name: Restaurante Origem
description: Outstanding tasty of the Brazilian cosine.

name: The Grove
description: A visual, gastronomic and service delight

name: Sails Restaurant
description: The cuisine at Sails is always delicious and beautifully presented. It's a great restaurant with a lovely outlook over Westhaven Marina and the harbour bridge.

name: PIC
description: A must try ;)

name: Ristorante Don Alfonso 1890
description: Exceptional experience, and one we'll always remember!

name: Akira Back
description: Dishes were delicious, inventive, and beautifully presented and the views on the 38th floor just above the restaurant were a nice end to our evening.

name: Maido
description: Noel Raimundo Decàn review of Maido

name: Lahaina Grill
description: This place is like home. It makes you feel like the most important guest. Food is exceptional and the service is fantastic.

name: 5 Gourmet Restaurant & Bar
description: Fantastic gourmet dinner in the heart of Stuttgart!!!

name: Chila
description: Buenos Aires' Degustation Adventure

name: Summer Pavilion
description: Impressive service, wonderful CNY dinner!

name: Tin Lung Heen
description: Attentive service makes the excellent food taste even better.

name: Mandarin Grill + Bar at Mandarin Oriental, Hong Kong
description: Brilliant food and service on birthday

name: Restaurante 1621
description: Dining at this beautiful location, with such a rich history was an incredible experience. The food on the tasting menu was phenomenal...

name: Tulemar Bungalows & Villas
description: The perfect vacation. The best part was simply chilling on our veranda, looking out at the ocean, watching parrots fly past.

name: Hotel Colline de France
description: Whether on a honeymoon or family vacation, you will fall in love with the hotel. It’s very nice, but what makes it truly special is not the expensive decor, it’s the staff!

name: Ikos Aria
description: An absolutely beautiful hotel in the most stunning of locations. With immaculately kept grounds, a wide sandy beach, crystal clear seas and views of the beautiful island.

name: Romance Istanbul Hotel
description: The geographical location is one thing, however this boutique hotel really excels at hospitality. Everyone was very friendly, the rooms were very clean and all of your wishes are fulfilled instantly.

name: THE OMNIA
description: Everything was perfect: the Bond-like cave entrance, the view from the terrace, the indoor/outdoor spa, the sensational service, the whisky selection, the unbelievable schnitzel…

name: Kayakapi Premium Caves - Cappadocia
description: It felt so special to not only stay in an original cave home, but also to experience the luxurious touches the hotel had added.

name: Six Senses Laamu
description: We were encouraged to go barefoot and it helped us feel connected to the earth. Loved stepping off our deck directly into the ocean to snorkel where the waters are teeming with beautiful marine life.

name: Hamanasi Adventure and Dive Resort
description: The service is really amazing. We thought they had all been sent to charm school. We've recommended this place to our friends and even our enemies.

name: Padma Resort Ubud
description: Wow just wow! The setting and location are just breathtaking! As soon as you set foot in the lounge, you are taken by the views of the beautiful jungle.

name: BLESS Hotel Madrid
description: Not only is the place classy, elegant, and dynamic, the staff is also top class. They made sure that our time at Bless was unique, memorable and unmatchable.

name: Ikos Dassia
description: The staff can’t seem to do enough for you, the restaurants, including the buffet, are very good, the place is spotless and the facilities are second to none.

name: Pimalai Resort and Spa
description: Brilliant experience

name: Lotte Hotel Hanoi
description: Sensational service - world class

name: COMO Cocoa Island
description: Perfect - a home away from home!

name: La Maison Favart
description: Absolutely great in every way! Very friendly and attentive staff, beautifully decorated rooms, a nice spa and very centrally located.

name: Sukhumvit Park, Bangkok - Marriott Executive Apartments
description: Super hospitality

name: Quinta Jardins do Lago
description: As near perfection as one could reasonably expect: quality and attention to detail; friendly, quietly efficient, but not intrusive, service; beautiful gardens and a delightful pool.

name: La Maison Arabe
description: Stay here and have an amazing trip!

name: The Royal Purnama
description: A perfect relaxing and inspiring hotel, a must!

name: Jaya House River Park
description: Laidback luxury…genuinely friendly not fake fussy.

name: The Hazelton Hotel
description: Welcoming Staff, Great Location

name: Round Hill Hotel and Villas
description: Spectacular!

name: Saraye Ameriha Boutique Hotel
description: Lovely ,nice ,traditional hotel in Kashan

name: Bucuti & Tara Beach Resort Aruba
description: The resort is beautiful, the service outstanding, and the wide, white sand beach is stunning. The staff made us feel special and pampered all week.

name: The Oberoi Beach Resort Sahl Hasheesh
description: Amazing place

name: Flagship Amsterdam Open Boat Canal Cruise - Local live guide with bar on board
description: Fun and informative and money well spent. Skipper and host were comical and enjoyable, telling us random but no less incredible facts about Amsterdam as we sailed through it.

name: Dubai: Red Dunes ATV, Sandsurf, Camels, Stargazing & 5* BBQ at Al Khayma Camp™️
description: The best experience in Dubai. Everything was perfect. The show, the quad, the 4x4 tour in the desert, sandboarding, the reception at the camp, the meal, our very friendly guide.

name: Tour of North Shore & Sightseeing
description: Our tour guide was awesome! He taught us so much about Hawaiian culture and history. The Waimea gardens and waterfall were gorgeous and definitely something you don't want to miss! Loved every minute!

name: Aruba Natural Pool and Indian Cave Jeep Safari
description: Amazing excursion - great introduction to the wonders of Aruba’s undeveloped side. Wonderful guide - knowledgeable, informative, personable, witty, helpful, and thoughtful. Excellent lunch included.

name: Clear Kayak Tour of Shell Key Preserve and Tampa Bay Area
description: What a wonderful and relaxing way to spend the day - kayaking in beautiful blue water and meandering in and out of mangroves. Our fabulous guide was full of information.

name: Classic Inca Trail Trek 4D/3N to Machu Picchu (Group Service)
description: Accomplishing this hike was made so much easier by Alpaca Expeditions, our guide, and the porters and chefs that came along. They are 100% local and indigenous-owned and are forerunners in sustainable tourism.

name: Reykjavik Food Walk - Local Foodie Adventure in Iceland
description: A perfect afternoon of eating, walking, and laughing. We were particularly impressed with the variety of restaurants: fancy, traditional and even street. Also timed well in that we never waited and never rushed.

name: High-Speed Thames River RIB Cruise in London
description: Exhilarating experience for the whole family!

name: Rafting - Brotas - Rio Jacare Pepira
description: Great memorable family experience!

name: City & Beatles Tour - BLUE ROUTE
description: Amazing bus tour with Chloe and Collin!

name: The Best tour in Florence: Renaissance & Medici Tales - guided by a STORYTELLER
description: A great way to learn more about how the Medici family shaped Florence. My tour guide did an excellent job turning complicated history into easy-to-follow stories.

name: Hot Air Balloons Ride in Luxor Egypt By HOD-HOD SOLIMAN
description: Loved it from beginning to end - so still up in the air, incredible views of the Valley of the Kings and several temples, and a stunning sunrise. Unbeatable!

name: Cappadocia Balloon Ride and Champagne Breakfast
description: A dream come true. The scenery was beautiful, and the flight was breathtaking. The entire crew of staff were professional and caring.

name: Little Havana Food and Walking Tour in Miami
description: Great food, great local history, and great new friends. A fun experience that I would definitely recommend as a way to get aquatinted with a new community.

name: Half-Day Mojave Desert ATV Tour from Las Vegas
description: Thoroughly enjoyed the entire tour. Detailed, funny, and most importantly very serious about our safety and gave a great experience that I would definitely do again!

name: The Chocolatarium Chocolate Tour Experience in Edinburgh
description: Hidden Gem of Edinburgh tourism

name: Cab tours belfast famous black taxi tours
description: Amazing!

name: Adventure Dubrovnik - Sea Kayaking and Snorkeling Tour
description: Best day yet!

name: Best of Istanbul: 1, 2 or 3-Day Private Guided Istanbul Tour
description: Great and flexible way to see the city

name: Chichen Itza, Cenote and Valladolid All-Inclusive Tour
description: Make the most of the drive to the ruins!

name: Dubai: Old and Modern City Tour with Blue Mosque Visit by OceanAir™️
description: Dubai : Went to the Yacht cruise with Oceaniar Tour Travel guide

name: Vespa Sidecar Tour in Rome with Cappuccino
description: Excellent! Best way to see Rome in style!

name: ABC Snorkel Charters Port Douglas Snorkelling max 12 passengers
description: Definitely a 10 Star Experience

name: Paragliding Oludeniz, Fethiye, Turkey
description: Brilliant experience. We took off from a snowy mountain, flew through a clear blue sky and landed on the beach.

name: Arenales Caves, River and Waterfall Plus Hidden Spring Full Day Adventure in PR
description: Adventures in nature
